featureType.title: Australian Depth Contours (Parks Australia NVCL depth zones)
featureType.abstract: Depth contours for 30, 70, 200, 700, 2000, 4000 and 6000m corresponding with the Parks Australia Natural Values Common Language (NVCL) depth zones for MERI/ME reporting. Contours derived from the Australian Bathymetric and Topography Grid, 2023 (Geoscience Australia). Styled for use on the Seamap Australia website.
